collectionMetadata.name: Employed Residents Aged 15 Years and Over by Industry, Age and Sex
collectionMetadata.description:
* Data are for mid-year.
* Residents refer to Singapore Citizens and Permanent Residents.
* Data are classified based on Singapore Standard Industrial Classification (SSIC) 2020. Data before year 2020 which were coded based on earlier versions of the SSIC were mapped to SSIC 2020 as far as possible to facilitate data comparability. 
* ' - ' : Nil or negligible.

Source: Comprehensive Labour Force Survey, Manpower Research And Statistics Department, MOM
